  "body": "Several reasons:\r\n\r\n* Allows to change the RNG lookahead (currently at least 1 epoch) without messing with the `BeaconState` format.\r\n* Allows to expose randomness as an opcode in the EVM 2.0 (similar to the `BLOCKHASH` opcode).\r\n* Useful for the VDF logic. (Note: the plan is to include VDF placeholders in the `BeaconState`.)",
